; PgBouncer auth file template — copy to userlist.txt and fill in real values.
; DO NOT commit the real userlist.txt (it contains password hashes).
;
; Format: "username" "md5<md5(password + username)>"
; Generate the hash with:
;   echo -n "<password><username>" | md5sum
; then prefix the output with "md5".
;
; Add one line per Postgres role that Cloud Functions / migration scripts
; connect as (matches rds.user in `firebase functions:config:get`), plus an
; admin user for PgBouncer's own console (SHOW POOLS, SHOW STATS, etc.).

"fufaji_app" "md5REPLACE_WITH_GENERATED_HASH"
"pgbouncer_admin" "md5REPLACE_WITH_GENERATED_HASH"
